{"word":"ἀγριότης","slug":"ἀγριότης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγριότης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγριος'><el>ἄγριος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>wildness, savageness</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in moral sense, <i>savageness, fierceness, cruelty</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}